OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1781799074
OL,3,C'Prime location' to host first stage
OL,4,Cof Tour of Britain Women
OL,6,FCockermouth has been announced as the
OL,7,Fhost of the first stage of the 2026
OL,8,FTour of Britain Women.
OL,10,FStage 1 on 19 August will see riders
OL,11,Fset off from Cockermouth before
OL,12,Fheading out west towards Whitehaven,
OL,13,FWorkington and Maryport, before
OL,14,Ffinishing back in the market town.
OL,16,FThe region has a strong history of
OL,17,Fhosting bike races, and has featured
OL,18,F12 stages of the Tour of Britain Men,
OL,19,Fmost recently in 2021.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
