PN,32102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1781799074
OL,3,C'Prime location' to host first stage
OL,4,Cof Tour of Britain Women
OL,6,FCockermouth itself has hosted the
OL,7,Fmen's race twice - in 2015 and 2018.
OL,9,FIn 2027, Cumbria will host two stages
OL,10,Fof the Tour de France Grand Depart,
OL,11,Fwith the first stage starting in
OL,12,FEdinburgh and finishing in Carlisle,
OL,13,Fbefore stage two leaving from Keswick
OL,14,Fand heading south to Liverpool.
OL,16,FThe Leader of Cumberland Council, Cllr
OL,17,FMark Fryer, said the Tour of Britain
OL,18,FWomen is another chance to show off
OL,19,Fwhat Cumbria has to offer.
OL,26,@rD@^rr
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
