OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,322,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1781799074
OL,3,C'Prime location' to host first stage
OL,4,Cof Tour of Britain Women
OL,6,FHe said: "Once again, we will be in
OL,7,Fthe global spotlight.
OL,9,F"This is great news for Cumberland and
OL,10,Ffollowing on from the announcement
OL,11,Fthat we will stage a finish and a
OL,12,Fstart of the Tour de France next year;
OL,13,Fthis is proof that our area is a prime
OL,14,Flocation for international events.
OL,16,F"This is a massive opportunity to
OL,17,Fshowcase our west coast and inspire
OL,18,Four communities to get active and see
OL,19,Fa world class event on their doorstep."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
