PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1781799074
OL,3,C'Prime location' to host first stage
OL,4,Cof Tour of Britain Women
OL,6,FThe race is made up of five stages,
OL,7,Fand will work its way south to finish
OL,8,Fin Royal Leamington Spa.
OL,10,FThe full list of stages is:
OL,12,FStage 1: Cockermouth - Cockermouth
OL,13,FStage 2: Clitheroe - BlackpoolJStage
OL,14,F3: Mold to The Great Orme, Llandudno
OL,15,FStage 4: Llanidloes to Hay-on-Wye
OL,16,FStage 5: Royal Leamington Spa ` Royal
OL,17,FLeamington Spa
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
