PN,32105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1781799074
OL,3,C'Prime location' to host first stage
OL,4,Cof Tour of Britain Women
OL,6,FBritish Cycling says its research
OL,7,Fshowed the 2025 race brought an
OL,8,Foverall economic benefit of #62.3
OL,9,Fmillion to the local areas which
OL,10,Fhosted the ten stages across the men
OL,11,Fand women's races.
OL,13,FJonathan Day, Director of Events for
OL,14,FBritish Cycling Ventures, said: "We
OL,15,Fare excited to be bringing the
OL,16,Fprestigious Lloyds Tour of Britain
OL,17,FWomen to these fantastic locations in
OL,18,FAugust.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
