PN,32106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1781799074
OL,3,C'Prime location' to host first stage
OL,4,Cof Tour of Britain Women
OL,6,F"For the first time, there is parity
OL,7,Fin the number of stages with the men's
OL,8,Frace a couple of weeks later, so it is
OL,9,Fa huge opportunity to create a real
OL,10,Ffestival of cycling, with the women's
OL,11,Frace kick-starting a brilliant few
OL,12,Fweeks of world class road racing."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/6
